Mad Hot Ballroom;;83;;84;;PG;;Documentary filmmaker Marilyn Agrelo chronicles the lives of several New York City schoolchildren as they get ready for a dancing competition sponsored by the nonprofit group American Ballroom Theater. As the finals of the competition near, the students -- ranging in age from 10 to 11 and coming from both poor and affluent neighborhoods -- make their transformation from reticent novices to confident contestants versed in the Latin styles of foxtrot, merengue and rumba.;;Documentary;;Marilyn Agrelo;;2005;;Heather Berman,Emma Therese Biegacki,Eva Carrozza,Evangelina Carrozzo,Paul Daggett;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mad_hot_ballroom